description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to react to the Bears trading for Nick Foles. The guys discuss why Chicago made the deal and what they gave up, before analyzing their impending QB competition and if Foles or Mitch Trubisky will be the 2020 Week 1 starter. The Pick Six Superfriends also discuss the move from the Jaguars' perspective and what it says about their commitment to Gardner Minshew. Finally, a quick glance at the remaining quarterback market.
